  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Today, there is an important lack of knowledge on the effects of dietary protein on protein
      metabolism after physical activity in children. Here, the investigators will measure changes
      in whole body protein metabolism using minimally invasive techniques and stable isotope
      methodology at rest and after physical activity with the intake of milk protein.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
